  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to identify factors associated with hyponatremia among patients
      hospitalized in the internal medicine ward. Consequtive patients hospitalized because of
      hyponatremia will be recruited. Follow up will include clinical factors such as background
      diseases, complete drug history, blood tests including Biochemistry tests (Sodium, renal
      function), endocrinological evaluation, thyroid function tests, cortisol,urinary sodium on
      addmition. One month following discharge follow up Sodium level will be taken.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
